キーチェーンなどとして使えます。どこにでも連れてってあげてください。
...and they can be used as keychains. Please take them with you everywhere!

773
01:04:05,096 --> 01:04:10,596
Next one is these badges, but they are a bit unusual because this time they are square...

774
01:04:10,596 --> 01:04:15,596
...and made from fake leather, so they're a bit squishy.

775
01:04:15,596 --> 01:04:18,596
And of course, you can make an ita-bag with these, too.

776
01:04:18,596 --> 01:04:23,096
今回のバッジはなんと、えーっと、フェイクレザーでできてますし、あと四角だし...
These badges are actually made of fake leather, and they are square...

777
01:04:23,096 --> 01:04:28,596
変わっておりますが、もちろんこれでも痛バッグとかできたりしますよ。
...which is unique, but of course you can use them to make an ita-bag!

778
01:04:28,596 --> 01:04:33,596
Last item is the smartphone ring, modeled after KFP chickens!

779
01:04:33,596 --> 01:04:38,596
Maybe this way, holding your phones won't be as hard with your wings. Cute!

780
01:04:38,596 --> 01:04:43,096
最後のアイテムはスマホリング！もちろんKFPモチーフです！<
The last item is a smartphone ring! Of course, it features a KFP motif!

781
01:04:43,096 --> 01:04:47,596
And besides that, there's also a voice pack.

782
01:04:47,596 --> 01:04:52,096
I haven't been doing any voice packs these past months, so make sure to get this one. Rare!

783
01:04:52,096 --> 01:04:56,096
その他には久しぶりにボイスもあります！
Other than that, there is also a voice pack after a long time!

784
