もちろん、いつも通りフルセットゲットすると、えー、ま、チェキ付いてきます！
Of course, as always, if you get the full set, you'll get an instant photo!

789
01:05:14,404 --> 01:05:16,904
限定版だとキアラのサイン入りですね！
If it's the limited edition, it will be signed by Kiara!

790
01:05:16,904 --> 01:05:19,904
よろしくお願いします！
Thank you in advance!

791
01:05:19,904 --> 01:05:23,104
One more thing before we end, I have a...

792
01:05:23,104 --> 01:05:26,604
